%% Diagram: CMAF shared segments across HLS and DASH
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart LR
    SRC[Source video] --> ENC[Encoder]
    ENC --> SEG[CMAF fMP4 segments<br/>.cmfv / .cmfa / .m4s]
    SEG --> HLS[HLS .m3u8 manifest]
    SEG --> DASH[DASH .mpd manifest]
    HLS --> SAFARI[Safari / iOS / tvOS]
    DASH --> CHROME[Chrome / Firefox / Edge / Android]
    HLS -.same bytes.-> SEG
    DASH -.same bytes.-> SEG
